ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisReappointment of ELLEN C. DESMOND of Rothesay, New Brunswick, as a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and her designation for the Atlantic region and Nunavut, effective July 20, 2025.
